0.1    First (alpha) release of the package, includes complete beam line
       and detector geometry, magnetic fields, and the built-in particle
       gun event generator.

0.2    Output to the hddm file specified in the OUTFILE line in control.in
       is now supported. The output hddm file contains a <reaction> tag with
       a full specification of the primary particles that were launched at
       the beginning of the simulation for each event.

0.3    Hits in the CDC are now being written to the output hddm file.
